108
00:06:03,840 --> 00:06:04,650
Fei Zhe.

109
00:06:05,250 --> 00:06:06,310
What are you doing?

110
00:06:07,280 --> 00:06:08,250
I plan to practice

111
00:06:08,250 --> 00:06:09,560
for another three hours every day.

112
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:10,880
I'll tell Xue Yiran

113
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:11,880
after I become stronger

114
00:06:11,880 --> 00:06:13,210
and give him a surprise.

115
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:14,800
Xue Yiran said

116
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:16,260
