117
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,760
Just believe him.

118
00:06:18,400 --> 00:06:19,370
I should have self-knowledge

119
00:06:19,370 --> 00:06:20,850
at least.

120
00:06:20,890 --> 00:06:21,930
No matter how strong Xue Yiran is,

121
00:06:21,930 --> 00:06:23,730
he can't lead a loser to victory.

122
00:06:24,570 --> 00:06:25,210
Fine.

123
00:06:25,210 --> 00:06:26,080
Keep going.

124
00:08:22,890 --> 00:08:24,080
There was a time

125
00:08:25,690 --> 00:08:26,830
when I thought

126
00:08:27,400 --> 00:08:29,460
I couldn't fulfill my promise to him.

127
00:08:30,090 --> 00:08:31,330
But your appearance

128
00:08:31,730 --> 00:08:32,679
made me feel

129
00:08:33,690 --> 00:08:35,000
maybe

130
00:08:35,530 --> 00:08:37,120
I can graduate with a smile.

131
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:52,220
If

132
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:54,370
it's at the cost of your sports career,

133
00:08:58,280 --> 00:08:58,750
I'd rather

134
00:08:58,750 --> 00:09:00,110
I had never shown up.

135
00:09:10,280 --> 00:09:11,450
Indeed.

136
00:09:12,730 --> 00:09:16,160
People laugh at me for being crazy.

137
00:09:19,290 --> 00:09:20,520
I laugh at others...

138
00:09:32,640 --> 00:09:34,100
for not understanding me.

139
00:09:43,520 --> 00:09:45,050
Actually, since I was a kid,

140
00:09:47,210 --> 00:09:48,730
I've been used to it.

141
00:09:51,410 --> 00:09:53,720
It seems I will lose everything I cherish

142
00:09:56,210 --> 00:09:58,320
one by one.

143
00:10:02,040 --> 00:10:03,170
When I was little,

144
00:10:04,650 --> 00:10:06,680
my favorite cat

145
00:10:09,090 --> 00:10:10,280
went missing.

146
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:15,080
My parents

147
00:10:15,940 --> 00:10:17,510
gave me a warm family.

148
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:20,020
But they divorced.

149
00:10:23,770 --> 00:10:24,890
My mom said

150
00:10:27,410 --> 00:10:28,650
she couldn't find me.

151
00:10:30,890 --> 00:10:31,680
But

152
00:10:33,850 --> 00:10:35,240
I only asked my uncle

153
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:38,970
and found out her phone number.

154
00:10:40,210 --> 00:10:41,010
Qi Tian.

155
00:10:44,170 --> 00:10:46,200
It's not that she couldn't find me.

156
00:10:51,330 --> 00:10:53,060
She just didn't want to find me.

157
00:10:58,290 --> 00:11:01,020
Fei Zhe organized a birthday celebration for me.

158
00:11:01,560 --> 00:11:02,960
It was

159
00:11:03,770 --> 00:11:05,300
the first time in my life...

160
00:11:06,490 --> 00:11:09,420
that someone volunteered to celebrate my birthday.

161
00:11:12,090 --> 00:11:13,000
Then...

162
00:11:16,330 --> 00:11:17,520
he passed away.

163
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:24,290
Last year,

164
00:11:27,330 --> 00:11:29,190
something was wrong with my foot.

165
00:11:31,730 --> 00:11:33,990
I thought I could hold on till I graduate.

166
00:11:36,770 --> 00:11:37,570
But

167
00:11:46,570 --> 00:11:47,360
it seems

168
00:11:48,710 --> 00:11:50,510
I will lose everything I cherish

169
00:11:51,690 --> 00:11:53,800
one by one.

170
00:11:57,130 --> 00:11:59,360
This seems to be the script of my life.

171
00:12:08,690 --> 00:12:09,800
I don't even know

172
00:12:11,280 --> 00:12:12,740
what else I deserve to have

173
00:12:14,680 --> 00:12:16,450
in my life.

174
00:12:42,330 --> 00:12:43,330
I understand him.

175
00:12:44,890 --> 00:12:46,760
After all, if he undergoes an operation,

176
00:12:46,760 --> 00:12:48,410
it will take a lot of time

177
00:12:48,680 --> 00:12:50,480
to recover to his current level.

178
00:12:51,480 --> 00:12:53,250
If he still insists,

179
00:12:55,170 --> 00:12:56,630
I'll leave the relay team.

180
00:12:58,530 --> 00:12:59,930
Graduating with a smile?

181
00:13:01,450 --> 00:13:03,000
What darn promise?

182
00:13:04,170 --> 00:13:05,300
If he loses his foot,

183
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:07,690
he'll lose everything.

184
00:13:08,170 --> 00:13:09,570
Now that I think about it,

185
00:13:09,680 --> 00:13:11,280
I also said a lot out of anger.

186
00:13:11,930 --> 00:13:13,250
Xue Yiran

187
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:15,850
must be under a lot of pressure.

188
00:13:18,760 --> 00:13:20,240
Fei Zhe had many friends.

189
00:13:21,170 --> 00:13:21,960
His death

190
00:13:22,690 --> 00:13:24,040
made everyone very sad.

191
00:13:25,010 --> 00:13:25,960
Xue Yiran

192
00:13:26,360 --> 00:13:27,330
naturally became

193
00:13:27,330 --> 00:13:29,330
the outlet for everyone's sadness.

194
00:13:30,960 --> 00:13:31,840
But actually,

195
00:13:32,570 --> 00:13:33,720
we forgot

196
00:13:35,730 --> 00:13:37,730
the one who was the closest to Fei Zhe

197
00:13:38,170 --> 00:13:39,600
was Xue Yiran.

198
00:13:44,920 --> 00:13:46,850
In fact, he was the saddest person.

199
00:13:47,650 --> 00:13:49,710
I don't know how he lived these years.

200
00:13:50,570 --> 00:13:52,300
It seems he is Prince Charming,

201
00:13:52,420 --> 00:13:53,280
but he has never had the mood

202
00:13:53,280 --> 00:13:54,480
to find a girlfriend.

203
00:13:55,800 --> 00:13:57,200
I think what he wants most

204
00:13:57,840 --> 00:13:58,680
is to get rid of the guilt

205
00:13:58,680 --> 00:14:00,340
that bothers him every day.

206
00:14:02,520 --> 00:14:03,980
But he loves running most.

207
00:14:04,840 --> 00:14:06,080
If he can't continue to run

208
00:14:06,080 --> 00:14:07,320
because of this...

209
00:14:09,280 --> 00:14:10,480
Do you think Xue Yiran

210
00:14:10,770 --> 00:14:11,810
is someone who would

211
00:14:11,810 --> 00:14:13,240
care about his ranking?

212
00:14:21,610 --> 00:14:22,530
Senior Shixing,

213
00:14:22,530 --> 00:14:23,480
the training must be tiring.

214
00:14:23,480 --> 00:14:24,410
Have some water.

215
00:14:24,690 --> 00:14:25,380
Thank you.

216
00:14:26,170 --> 00:14:27,490
He is so handsome.

217
00:14:27,520 --> 00:14:29,650
How long have you been training today?

218
00:14:30,290 --> 00:14:32,220
I've been training for a long time.

219
00:14:32,610 --> 00:14:33,890
You must be very tired.

220
00:14:35,210 --> 00:14:36,070
Are you hungry?

221
00:14:37,490 --> 00:14:38,330
A little.

222
00:14:39,640 --> 00:14:41,850
We'll bring you some food later.

223
00:14:43,400 --> 00:14:44,200
Shen Ming.

224
00:14:44,660 --> 00:14:45,460
Ms. Luo.

225
00:14:45,650 --> 00:14:46,880
Who are those two girls?

226
00:14:46,880 --> 00:14:47,720
Those two...

227
00:14:48,030 --> 00:14:49,110
are Xing's fans.

228
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:50,890
Fans?

229
00:14:51,370 --> 00:14:52,810
He has fans?

230
00:14:53,160 --> 00:14:53,920
Let me tell you.

231
00:14:53,920 --> 00:14:55,370
Xing looks more handsome

232
00:14:55,400 --> 00:14:56,570
after shaving his beard.

233
00:14:56,570 --> 00:14:57,520
Also, he is a top student

234
00:14:57,520 --> 00:14:58,530
and excels in sports.

235
00:14:58,530 --> 00:15:00,730
It's normal for him to have fans, right?

236
00:15:02,050 --> 00:15:02,290
Alright.

237
00:15:02,290 --> 00:15:03,000
I'm getting back to running.

238
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:03,610
Okay.

239
00:15:05,760 --> 00:15:06,890
The training is so tiring.

240
00:15:06,890 --> 00:15:07,680
You should look after your health.

241
00:15:07,680 --> 00:15:09,280
-Zeng Shixing.
-That's right. Otherwise, we'll be worried.

242
00:15:09,280 --> 00:15:10,080
Zeng Shixing.

243
00:15:11,400 --> 00:15:12,330
Come here.

244
00:15:12,680 --> 00:15:13,490
What's wrong?

245
00:15:13,850 --> 00:15:15,330
-We're leaving then.
-Come here.

246
00:15:15,330 --> 00:15:16,810
I'm a doctor.

247
00:15:16,850 --> 00:15:17,850
Of course I asked you here for a health checkup.

248
00:15:17,850 --> 00:15:19,030
-Senior, bye.
-Bye.

249
00:15:41,280 --> 00:15:42,080
Get down.

250
00:15:43,530 --> 00:15:44,600
Why?

251
00:15:46,210 --> 00:15:48,210
Didn't you say

252
00:15:48,240 --> 00:15:50,370
you strained your glutes a few days ago?

253
00:15:50,370 --> 00:15:51,470
I made it up

254
00:15:51,650 --> 00:15:53,040
to seduce you.

255
00:15:54,370 --> 00:15:55,600
I knew it.

256
00:15:58,960 --> 00:15:59,560
Why didn't you send me messages

257
00:15:59,560 --> 00:16:00,930
these days?

258
00:16:00,930 --> 00:16:01,970
I didn't want to.

259
00:16:02,170 --> 00:16:02,960
I'm tired.

260
00:16:03,920 --> 00:16:05,780
Then why did you shave your beard?

261
00:16:06,210 --> 00:16:07,670
I was trying to look older,

262
00:16:07,720 --> 00:16:08,790
but it didn't work.

263
00:16:10,410 --> 00:16:11,870
I've decided to be myself.

264
00:16:14,330 --> 00:16:16,190
You don't like me anymore, right?

265
00:16:19,300 --> 00:16:20,110
I'm tired of it.

266
00:16:20,110 --> 00:16:21,030
Tired?

267
00:16:21,590 --> 00:16:22,480
What do you mean?

268
00:16:22,480 --> 00:16:24,140
Now you are tired of me, right?

269
00:16:25,090 --> 00:16:26,810
Why do you have so many questions?

270
00:16:26,810 --> 00:16:28,090
Should I answer all your questions

271
00:16:28,090 --> 00:16:30,020
just because you're older than me?

272
00:16:30,880 --> 00:16:31,720
Zeng Shixing,

273
00:16:32,010 --> 00:16:33,670
now you've learned to talk back, right?

274
00:16:33,670 --> 00:16:34,870
I said I'm tired of it.

275
00:16:34,970 --> 00:16:36,680
I have a headache whenever I see you.

276
00:16:36,680 --> 00:16:37,960
I'm going to beat you.

277
00:16:56,590 --> 00:16:57,990
Don't make another move.

278
00:16:58,650 --> 00:16:59,880
I can't guarantee

279
00:16:59,880 --> 00:17:01,520
what I'm going to do next.

280
00:17:04,520 --> 00:17:08,450
Who I'm tired of is myself who's always worried about gains and losses,

281
00:17:08,599 --> 00:17:09,410
not you.

282
00:17:16,319 --> 00:17:17,210
Ms. Luo,

283
00:17:17,210 --> 00:17:18,000
are you here?

284
00:17:24,490 --> 00:17:28,280
♫They said where I should turn my face to♫

285
00:17:28,319 --> 00:17:32,800
♫They said where I should look at♫

286
00:17:28,410 --> 00:17:29,820
It's a clean shave.

