00:20:29,130 --> 00:20:30,720
Finally, I left this boring place.

331
00:20:30,720 --> 00:20:32,250
What should we eat tonight?

332
00:20:32,960 --> 00:20:33,680
Tonight,

333
00:20:33,680 --> 00:20:34,750
why don't we ask Tianfu,

334
00:20:34,750 --> 00:20:36,190
Ziji, and Fatty

335
00:20:36,230 --> 00:20:37,630
to have hot pot together?

336
00:20:41,640 --> 00:20:43,560
You can't get angry

337
00:20:43,560 --> 00:20:45,760
just because I won't have an operation.

338
00:20:46,880 --> 00:20:48,320
It's your foot.

339
00:20:48,450 --> 00:20:49,580
Why would I be angry?

340
00:20:50,520 --> 00:20:51,910
But you look like

341
00:20:51,990 --> 00:20:53,180
you're angry.

342
00:21:06,570 --> 00:21:07,330
Sir,

343
00:21:07,370 --> 00:21:08,410
you're driving towards the wrong direction.

344
00:21:08,410 --> 00:21:08,850
This is not the direction

345
00:21:08,850 --> 00:21:10,290
to Xinghe University.

346
00:21:10,290 --> 00:21:11,600
Sir, don't listen to him.

347
00:21:11,600 --> 00:21:13,490
Just drive according to the address I gave you.

348
00:21:13,490 --> 00:21:14,490
You kidnapped me.

349
00:21:14,690 --> 00:21:16,020
Where are you taking me?

350
00:21:18,050 --> 00:21:18,830
Are you taking me

351
00:21:18,830 --> 00:21:20,050
to the hospital for an operation?

352
00:21:20,050 --> 00:21:20,610
Sir,

353
00:21:20,610 --> 00:21:21,490
drop me off.

354
00:21:22,820 --> 00:21:24,820
You can barely move.

355
00:21:25,090 --> 00:21:25,920
If we drop you off now,

356
00:21:25,920 --> 00:21:26,850
where can you go?

357
00:21:29,540 --> 00:21:30,690
You'll know when we get there.

358
00:21:30,690 --> 00:21:32,890
I'm not taking you to have an operation.

359
00:22:03,060 --> 00:22:04,190
Isn't this place...

360
00:22:06,010 --> 00:22:07,410
Why did you bring me here?

361
00:22:08,030 --> 00:22:08,890
To recuperate?

362
00:22:15,200 --> 00:22:16,000
Let's go.

363
00:22:16,520 --> 00:22:18,580
Wang has arranged everything for us.

364
00:22:19,850 --> 00:22:21,730
Wang knows you brought me here?

365
00:22:22,480 --> 00:22:24,090
The car was prepared by Fatty.

366
00:22:24,090 --> 00:22:25,370
You Qian?

367
00:22:35,960 --> 00:22:37,160
Do you still remember

368
00:22:38,070 --> 00:22:39,430
we spent a night

369
00:22:39,450 --> 00:22:40,780
in He Miao's bathhouse?

370
00:22:43,610 --> 00:22:44,730
You asked me

371
00:22:46,040 --> 00:22:48,010
if you needed to meditate with me.

372
00:22:49,730 --> 00:22:50,410
Yes.

373
00:22:51,170 --> 00:22:52,750
You said I didn't need to do that,

374
00:22:52,750 --> 00:22:54,210
but you didn't tell me why.

375
00:22:57,050 --> 00:22:57,840
Yes.

376
00:22:59,410 --> 00:23:00,690
I was jealous.

377
00:23:01,800 --> 00:23:03,600
I didn't want you to be too happy.

378
00:23:04,930 --> 00:23:06,500
Now I can tell you why.

379
00:23:08,050 --> 00:23:08,650
Well...

380
00:23:08,650 --> 00:23:09,850
what about Xue Yiran?

381
00:23:10,330 --> 00:23:11,680
Does he need to meditate here

382
00:23:11,680 --> 00:23:12,760
like me?

383
00:23:18,340 --> 00:23:19,320
In this world,

384
00:23:20,440 --> 00:23:22,100
there are many types of people

385
00:23:22,130 --> 00:23:23,480
and brains.

386
00:23:23,990 --> 00:23:26,220
Some people are naturally reliant

387
00:23:26,260 --> 00:23:28,320
on emotions to motivate themselves.

388
00:23:29,410 --> 00:23:31,250
Let's take Wu Tianfu as an example.

389
00:23:31,250 --> 00:23:35,250
His results in individual races were not as good as those in relay races.

390
00:23:35,540 --> 00:23:36,620
Because teammates

391
00:23:37,290 --> 00:23:39,040
can stimulate his potential.

392
00:23:41,010 --> 00:23:41,850
But Xue Yiran

393
00:23:42,000 --> 00:23:44,000
is the type of people in the minority

394
00:23:44,070 --> 00:23:45,320
who can directly enter the ZONE state

395
00:23:45,320 --> 00:23:47,530
as soon as he stands on the track.

396
00:23:50,250 --> 00:23:52,530
Because he was born with a strong heart.

397
00:23:54,300 --> 00:23:56,500
Stage fright has nothing to do with him.

398
00:23:57,960 --> 00:23:58,850
He is perfect

399
00:24:00,690 --> 00:24:02,740
for heavyweight competitions.

400
00:24:04,350 --> 00:24:05,290
I don't know

401
00:24:05,480 --> 00:24:06,880
what he has been through.

402
00:24:07,880 --> 00:24:08,680
Maybe

403
00:24:09,350 --> 00:24:11,220
he has already suffered a lot.

404
00:24:12,930 --> 00:24:14,330
Usually, people like him

405
00:24:14,610 --> 00:24:16,680
were already under a lot of pressure

406
00:24:17,430 --> 00:24:19,240
when they were little.

407
00:24:23,400 --> 00:24:26,320
Their brains have become very resilient to pressure

408
00:24:26,320 --> 00:24:29,040
before they know it.

409
00:24:30,720 --> 00:24:31,580
So,

410
00:24:32,800 --> 00:24:33,830
usually, you don't know

411
00:24:33,830 --> 00:24:35,470
what is on Xue Yiran's mind.

412
00:24:36,130 --> 00:24:38,000
He doesn't show his emotions easily.

413
00:24:38,000 --> 00:24:39,330
He always wears a smile.

414
00:24:41,130 --> 00:24:42,990
No matter how big the occasion is,

415
00:24:43,310 --> 00:24:45,310
it doesn't matter to him.

416
00:24:52,050 --> 00:24:53,840
Do you know how much I envy you?

417
00:24:55,210 --> 00:24:57,630
You were born with a strong heart.

418
00:24:58,850 --> 00:24:59,650
But I

419
00:25:00,450 --> 00:25:03,510
have to go through a lot to have it.

420
00:25:10,810 --> 00:25:11,610
But...

421
00:25:13,250 --> 00:25:14,400
so what?

422
00:25:16,850 --> 00:25:18,130
I will lose

423
00:25:19,320 --> 00:25:20,510
what I like

424
00:25:22,730 --> 00:25:23,810
and cherish.

425
00:25:26,200 --> 00:25:27,770
Even if I have an operation,

426
00:25:30,730 --> 00:25:31,880
I'll have to leave

427
00:25:33,150 --> 00:25:34,430
the tracks.

428
00:25:38,330 --> 00:25:39,400
All I have left

429
00:25:40,460 --> 00:25:41,500
is my promise.

430
00:25:43,730 --> 00:25:44,880
All I can catch

431
00:25:46,640 --> 00:25:48,040
is also my promise.

432
00:25:55,200 --> 00:25:56,080
No.

433
00:25:58,450 --> 00:25:59,710
The script of your life

434
00:26:00,610 --> 00:26:01,610
is not losing.

435
00:26:03,570 --> 00:26:05,030
Just because of the people

436
00:26:05,720 --> 00:26:06,900
and things

437
00:26:07,800 --> 00:26:09,320
that made you suffer

438
00:26:09,720 --> 00:26:11,050
and left you in the past,

439
00:26:11,160 --> 00:26:11,960
you

440
00:26:12,840 --> 00:26:13,500
have gained

441
00:26:17,010 --> 00:26:18,940
a brain very resilient to pressure

442
00:26:19,250 --> 00:26:20,150
and a strong heart

443
00:26:20,150 --> 00:26:21,780
that make

444
00:26:22,580 --> 00:26:24,120
every athlete

445
00:26:24,400 --> 00:26:26,320
envious.

446
00:26:31,530 --> 00:26:32,570
Misfortune

447
00:26:33,850 --> 00:26:35,090
might be

448
00:26:35,720 --> 00:26:37,130
a blessing

449
00:26:37,970 --> 00:26:39,560
in disguise.

450
00:26:44,330 --> 00:26:45,130
So,

451
00:26:46,360 --> 00:26:47,360
don't always think about losing

452
00:26:47,360 --> 00:26:49,730
and live pessimistically.

453
00:26:51,280 --> 00:26:52,480
Go have an operation.

454
00:26:53,800 --> 00:26:55,730
We'll help you win the competition

455
00:26:55,840 --> 00:26:56,920
in August.

456
00:26:57,880 --> 00:26:59,250
Let's win together.

457
00:27:03,220 --> 00:27:04,020
How?

458
00:27:05,400 --> 00:27:07,530
