00:27:25,570 --> 00:27:27,370
I think I can lead you to victory,

465
00:27:27,460 --> 00:27:29,300
just like you thought

466
00:27:31,000 --> 00:27:33,400
you could lead Fei Zhe to victory back then.

467
00:27:48,320 --> 00:27:49,520
Do you think Xue Yiran

