00:28:07,640 --> 00:28:09,040
You told me so much today.

474
00:28:12,570 --> 00:28:13,560
I can only say

475
00:28:14,250 --> 00:28:16,450
I understand why he made this decision.

476
00:28:18,010 --> 00:28:19,160
But it doesn't mean I'll let him

477
00:28:19,160 --> 00:28:21,220
do something that will hurt himself.

478
00:28:21,520 --> 00:28:22,320
Because

479
00:28:24,170 --> 00:28:25,320
I can't forget

